I"$<ol>
  <li>Enable passwordless <strong>sudo</strong> access for the <code class="highlighter-rouge">rsync</code> command on the remote machine: <code class="highlighter-rouge">visudo</code>
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>&lt;$USER&gt; ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD: /usr/bin/rsync
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Transfer files from the remote machine with sudo access:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>rsync <span class="nt">--progress</span> <span class="nt">-rave</span> <span class="s1">'ssh'</span> <span class="nt">--rsync-path</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s1">'sudo rsync'</span> &lt;<span class="nv">$REMOTE_USER</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>@&lt;<span class="nv">$REMOTE_SERVER</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>:&lt;<span class="nv">$REMOTE_SOURCE</span><span class="o">&gt;</span> &lt;<span class="nv">$LOCAL_DESTINATION</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>

